American rapper, songwriter, and television personality, Belcalis Marlenis Almánzar popularly known as Cardi B, has revealed late rapper DMX is definitely in heaven. The sensational female rapper took to her twitter account hours after the death of Def jam rapper to say despite the many battles and obstacles the late rapper encountered, his faith in God stayed unwavering. The mother of one who joined billions of well-wishers all over the globe in mourning DMX said she knows for sure the late DMX is in heaven as God has been listening to all his supplications over the years. She tweeted: “No matter the battles and obstacles DMX was facing and going thru he never let his faith in God go.I know he is in heaven and I know the Lord been hearing his prayers for years and he is now in peace .RIP DMX.”